      <title>俄罗斯誓言对黑海上空的美国无人机采取措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/russia-vows-to-take-measures-against-us-drones-over-black-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯国防部长安德烈·别洛乌索夫指示陆军总参谋部对黑海上空的美国无人机采取“快速反应措施”，因为美国无人机的活动日益频繁，增加了空域发生事件的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/russia-vows-to-take-measures-against-us-drones-over-black-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 04:42:25 GMT</pubDate>
